### 1️⃣ ADD USER
POST http://localhost:8080/users/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rounak",
  "email": "rounak@gmail.com",
  "password": "1234"
}

###

### 2️⃣ ADD EXERCISE
POST http://localhost:8080/exercise/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bench Press",
  "muscleGroup": "Chest"
}

###

### 3️⃣ GET ALL EXERCISES
GET http://localhost:8080/exercise/all

###

### 4️⃣ GET EXERCISE BY MUSCLE
GET http://localhost:8080/exercise/muscle/Chest

###

### 5️⃣ CREATE WORKOUT (User ID = 1)
POST http://localhost:8080/workout/create/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "day": "Chest Day"
}

###

### 6️⃣ ADD WORKOUT ENTRY
### (Workout ID = 1, Exercise ID = 1)
POST http://localhost:8080/entry/add/1/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sets": 3,
  "reps": 10,
  "weight": 80
}

###

### 7️⃣ GET ALL WORKOUTS (BASIC)
GET http://localhost:8080/workout/all

###

### 8️⃣ GET FULL DETAILS (DTO OUTPUT 🔥)
GET http://localhost:8080/workout/details